    public class Mobile

    • Constructor Detail

      • Mobile

        public Mobile(String imei,
              String cellId,
              String iccid)
        This is the partial constructor for c8y_Mobile as described in the device management library.
        Parameters:
        imei - the International Mobile Equipment Number.
        cellId - the identifier of the current cell tower.
        iccid - the Integrated Curcuit Identifier.

      • Mobile

        public Mobile(String imsi,
              String imei,
              String currentOperator,
              String currentBand,
              String connType,
              String rssi,
              String ecn0,
              String rcsp,
              String mnc,
              String lac,
              String cellId,
              String msisdn,
              String iccid)
        This is the full constructor for c8y_Mobile as described in the sensor library.
        Parameters:
        imsi - the International Mobile Subscriber Identifier.
        imei - the International Mobile Equipment Number.
        currentOperator - the received mobile operator string, e.g. Telekom.
        currentBand - the current mobile band, e.g. WCDMA2100.
        connType - the current connection type, e.g. 3g
        rssi - the Receive Signal Strength Indicator value as text.
        ecn0 - EcNo is the RSCP divided by the RSSI
        rcsp - Received Signal Code Power as text.
        mnc - the Mobile Network Code, e.g. 1 (for Telekom Deutschland).
        lac - Location Area Code, e.g. 38833 (for Bonn Area in Telekom Deutschland network).
        cellId - the identifier of the current cell tower.
        msisdn - the Mobile Station Integrated Services Digital Network Number.
        iccid - the Integrated Curcuit Identifier.
